00:17:49.259 --> 00:17:50.210
Now, why is that?
 

00:17:50.210 --> 00:17:55.654
Well, because at time 0 over
here no one discounts the

00:17:55.654 --> 00:17:56.578
future.
 

00:17:56.578 --> 00:17:59.078
Gold at the beginning is worth
exact--

00:17:59.078 --> 00:18:02.195
