the beginning is the same as a

00:18:02.195 --> 00:18:05.057
unit of gold at the end in both
states because everyone's

00:18:05.057 --> 00:18:06.589
probabilities add up to 1.
 

00:18:06.589 --> 00:18:08.818
H (1 - H) is 1.
 

00:18:08.818 --> 00:18:11.595
So you might as well consume at
the beginning or for sure at the

00:18:11.595 --> 00:18:11.858
