00:29:32.578 --> 00:29:35.300
two period model,
which is what about the (.3,

00:29:35.300 --> 00:29:36.269
.3) promise?
 

00:29:36.269 --> 00:29:39.539
The optimist, H equals 1.
 

00:29:39.539 --> 00:29:40.650
Take that guy.
 

00:29:40.650 --> 00:29:44.220
He says to himself,
"I can't lose.

00:29:44.220 --> 00:29:55.498
Why should I be satisfied with
only promising (.2,

00:29:55.498 --> 00:29:56.880
.2)?
 

00:29:56.880 --> 00:29:59.942
Why don't I make a bigger
promise like (.3,

00:29:59.942 --> 00:30:00.380
.3).
 

00:30:00.380 --> 00:30:03.890
With my bigger promise I get
more money today,

00:30:03.890 --> 00:30:11.834
and with that extra money today
